	mapping inMM1::IotSystem::intermediate_unionEnterActor2Expression(expr :TimeModel::CCSLModel::ClockExpressionAndRelation::Expression , an : Actor, nb : Integer):TimeModel::CCSLModel::ClockExpressionAndRelation::Expression
	{
